overview: Two girls (Tasha Rain & Ana Morna) come looking to make it in LA, instead wind up working as cleaning girls at a budget motel when I.C.E. agents raid the place. Meeting a very vivacious happy party girl (Katie Morgan), the girls soon find themselves on a wild sexual adventure as they hop from one motel room to the other with an assortment of sexual partners. With a horned out motel manager (Evan Stone) and a cleaning staff supervisor who is on their butts all the time the laughs and the cum flies.
title: Party Girl
